<H1>rhosts: Tip</H1>

<P>To save time creating and maintaining different versions
of the the <STRONG>.rhosts</STRONG> file on each remote system:</P>

<P><STRONG>1.</STRONG> Create a <STRONG>.rhosts</STRONG> file with an entry for each
system that you have an account on.</P>

<P><STRONG>2.</STRONG> Copy this file to your home directory on each remote
host.</P>

